BACK UP YOUR FILES
My youtube how-to video:
http://youtu.be/OVoVbeBbV-o

If your hard drive is not shown in My Computer, or is not found or does not appear, then it's a fairly simple job to fix the "not detected" problem in the Computer Management Console. This is the short version of how to repair the problem by Initializing the hard drive in Disk Management, with added links showing how to repair or, as a last-hope effort, delete the MBR.




